   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>To change the LCM settings, go to the <uicontrol>Life Cycle
Monitoring LCM </uicontrol> screen.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Press 1 followed by the <uicontrol>ENTER</uicontrol> key
to go to the <uicontrol>Life Cycle Monitoring LCM â€“ Actions</uicontrol> screen.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Type in the action number of the setting to be changed
from the list in <xref href="Service_Serviceport_LCM_Action_Menu_REF_0000116582.xml"
                     format="dita"
                     scope="local"
                     type="reference"/> and press the <uicontrol>ENTER</uicontrol> key. The actual value is now displayed on the screen.</p>
            <stepxmp>
               <table>
                  <tgroup cols="1">
                     <colspec colname="col1"/>
                     <tbody>
                        <row>
                           <entry>
                              <screen xml:space="preserve">Type in action (3 characters '000') and press'ENTER':(Press 'ESC' to exit)&gt;Selected action:        026Actual parameter value: 120Type in the new parameter value and press 'ENTER':(Press 'ESC' to exit)&gt;</screen>
                           </entry>
                        </row>
                     </tbody>
                  </tgroup>
               </table>
            </stepxmp>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>To change the setting, type in the new setting parameter
and press the <uicontrol>ENTER</uicontrol> key.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
